net.akami.mask.function

Interface TrigonometryOperation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CosineFunction, SinusFunction, TangentFunction

    public interface TrigonometryOperation
    Util interface avoiding repetitions inside the trigonometric functions.

    Might not be required anymore after the expression system is finished.

      • trigonometricOperation

        default java.lang.String trigonometricOperation(java.lang.String input,
                                                char opChar)
        Computes a trigonometric operation from the given input and the given binding.

        Does not compute anything if the input is not a number.

        Parameters:
        input - the input given, to which the operation is to be applied
        opChar - the binding corresponding to the trigonometric operation
        Returns:
        the result of the calculation
